flowchart TD
    A[Start CFD Simulation] --> B{Problem Type?}
    B -->|Steady-State| C[Use SIMPLE]
    B -->|Transient| D[Use PISO]
    
    C --> E[Under-relaxation needed?]
    E -->|Yes| F[α_U=0.7, α_p=0.3]
    E -->|No| G[May diverge]
    F --> H[Iterate to convergence]
    
    D --> I[Time accuracy critical?]
    I -->|Yes| J[Use 3-5 PISO correctors]
    I -->|No| K[Use 2 PISO correctors]
    J --> L[Tight coupling per time step]
    K --> M[Moderate coupling]
    
    H --> N[Check residuals < 1e-6]
    L --> N
    M --> N
    N --> O[Solution Complete]
    
    style C fill:#e8f5e8
    style D fill:#e1f5fe